                "id": 32,
                "title": "August Wine Walks",
                "blog": "<div style=\"\n    background-color: #fff;\">\n\n    <article style=\"\n    background-color: #fff;\n    font:  400 16px/1.6 'Estandar-Regular', sans-serif;\n    color: #000;\n\"/>\n        </br>\n<div>\n    <strong>Wine Walks August 2023</strong>\n</br>\n<p>\n    Wow! Is August a busy month for local wines or what? Like wines and wineries there are so many options this time of\n    year. Life is short so try them all!! Regardless if you can make these events or not, be sure to sign up and get\n    these collections for later.\n    <br />\n    <br />\n    We are supporting two local walks for August featuring\n</p>\n    <div class=\"separator\">\n        <h2>Redmond August 4th, 2023</h2>\n    </div>\n    <p><strong>As of this Wednesday August 2nd there are still tickets available for the</strong>\n        <a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/e/2023-redmond-wine-walk-tickets-661378981337?aff=oddtdtcreator\"/>Redmond Wine Walk</a></p>\n    <p>\n        Our highlight winery for the Redmond wine walk is Drum Roll Wine. I talked with winemaker Matt Frazier at the\n        Snohomish Wine Festival and really got a feel for how much fun they have in the business. Make sure you check\n        out the link on WildAlmonds to their Music Video.\n    </p>\n    <figure class=\"align-center\">\n        <img\n                style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%\"\n                src=\"https://wildalmonds.com/api/uploads/6d237f72-8b91-45d6-be7b-cc62ae257bd8_redmondWineWalk.png\"\n                alt=\"Redmond Wine Walk\"\n        />\n        <figcaption class=\"blogFig\">Redmond wineries</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <div class=\"separator\">\n        <h2>Edmonds August 5th, 2023</h2>\n    </div>\n    <p><strong>Tickets sold out for the Edmonds event!!</strong></p>\n    <p>\n        The Edmonds Art Walk events are proving to be extremely popular with this latest event again sold out! I\n        talked with the director of this non-profit organization and could not be happier for them that these are in\n        demand.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        Attending this and the Redmond event is Michael Florentino Cellars. They are also involved in Sherman winery if\n        you have had them. Not only are they doing these wine walks, they are hosting a pairing event for members on\n        August 19th. Non-members can participate for $25 and $15 waved with purchase! We hope to be supporting that\n        event as well as on the end of September. More to come! Thank you for your support Michael Florentino!!\n    </p>\n    <figure class=\"align-center\">\n        <img\n                style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%\"\n                src=\"https://wildalmonds.com/api/uploads/450bec59-d09b-45b8-9535-fdea2ff94da5_edmondsWineWalkFull.png\"\n                alt=\"Edmonds Wine Walk\"\n        />\n        <figcaption class=\"blogFig\">Edmonds wineries</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n<p>\n    Refer to the WildAlmonds <a href=\"https://wildalmonds.com/api/uploads/0e34d0ba-7edb-414c-8b7e-08a632674f46_howToMay23.png\">\n    Quick Start</a> guide for an introduction if you need.\n</p>\n    <p>\n        Signup below to get your own Invitation to these wine walks!\n    </p>\n</div>\n</br>\n</div>",
