                "blog": "<div style=\"\n    background-color: #fff;\">\n\n    <article style=\"\n    background-color: #fff;\n    font:  400 16px/1.6 'Estandar-Regular', sans-serif;\n    color: #000;\n\"/>\n        </br>\n<div>\n    <strong>Kingston Wine & Brew fest</strong>\n</br>\n<p>\n    For a limited time, we are offering multiple wines on the platform in a single invitation! WildAlmonds has also been\n    supporting community events and getting a great response.\n    <br />\n</p>\n    <p>\n    As a taster, our platform allows you to navigate and comment on several wineries. Where we have expanded support\n    with a winery you can comment on their wines as well! This summer we have attended events at the Snohomish Wine Walk\n    and the Kirkland pour with Pride. We are also running a trial of our WildAlmonds home tile. From this tile you can\n        discover wineries in Lake Chelan, on the Kitsap Penninsula, and Woodinville.\n    </p>\n    <figure class=\"align-center\">\n        <img\n                style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%\"\n                src=\"https://wildalmonds.com/api/uploads/61fb48ff-38b3-4829-831f-891771cee23f_1000x300_Shared-Dream_horizontal.jpg\"\n                alt=\"Shared Dream\"\n        />\n        <figcaption class=\"blogFig\">Don't miss this one!</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p>\n    Our highlight winery for the Kingston Wine and Brew Fest is Shared Dream winery. I talked with winemaker Ken Dalgleish\n        about the Kingston event and how running a winery has been 'on the other side'. My extended family has had\n        a place on Marrowstone Island since before I was born and some of my very best memories are there. Shared Dream\n        winery is thriving from this location.\n    <figure class=\"align-center\">\n        <img\n                style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%\"\n                src=\"https://wildalmonds.com/api/uploads/0f98b500-81d6-4079-9288-8445738c3749_sharedDreamCollection.png\"\n                alt=\"Collection\"\n        />\n        <figcaption class=\"blogFig\">Shared Dream</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n        They will be bringing some wines you may not get a chance to try again!\n        Their 2021 Petit Verdot is a Seattle Wine Awards Gold and is Sold Out! Make sure you find Shared Dream Cellars\n        and try their wines before they're gone as well.\n    </p>\n<p>\n    Refer to the <a href=\"https://wildalmonds.com/api/uploads/0e34d0ba-7edb-414c-8b7e-08a632674f46_howToMay23.png\">\n    Quick Start</a> guide for an introduction.\n</p>\n    <p>\n        Signup to get your own Kingston Wine and Brew fest collection!\n    </p>\n</div>\n</br>\n</div>",
