                "id": 20,
                "title": "Pumpkin Contest 2022!!!",
                "blog": "<h1>Pumpkins 2022</h1>\n</br>\n<p>\n</br>\n</p>\n<p>\n    One of the principles of WildAlmonds has always been to make engagement more fun. We have had several users comment\n    that ‘we love how you’ve added gamification to your platform.’ It’s always a surprising comment for me to hear\n    because I don’t really consider it an effort to make it fun. It should be just built in and central to design or\n    why do it? Gamification sounds like hard work with fun as an afterthought to me.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n    A very early use of the platform was for pumpkin carving contest. This was early in the creation of the platform,\n    and the feedback we got was integral to several improvements. We skipped one last year, and heard from several of\n    those early adopters that we should run it again.\n    </p>\n    <img\n        id=left-image\n        src=\"https://wildalmonds.com/api/uploads/39d10c3c-8fbe-4ca3-8323-915a4d97757f_pumpkins2020.jpg\"\n        alt=\"pumpkins\"\n    />\n    <p>\n    </br>\n    Sounds like fun! We will be offering gift certificate prizes for two winners.\n    This will be good news if you are like me and are not very artistic as you can win by judging.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n    <strong>Prize #1   Be a carver:</strong>\n        <strong></strong>Simply carve a pumpkin and take a picture of it lit up. Submit the following <strong>before\n        October 31st</strong> by emailing us at support@wildalmonds.com\n     <ul>\n        <li>Pumpkin Name:</li>\n        <li>Pumpkin Description (optional):</li>\n        <li>Photo (your photo will be condensed to 300px by 300px in the square and expandable by judgers)</li>\n        <li>If you receive the most points, you win the event!</li>\n        <li>In the case of a tie, your WildAlmond value will serve as the tie-breaker. Highest value wins</li>\n        <li>You cannot vote for your own pumpkin!</li>\n    </ul>\n\n<p>\n    <strong>Prize #2    Be a judge:</strong>\n    Email us at support@wildalmonds.com and make sure to rank and Lock your top 4 pumpkins <strong>before November 5th</strong>\n    </br>\n    How does the judging work?\n    <ul>\n        <li>You will get an email containing a special unique link only for you to access the event.</li>\n        <li>Using the Almonds, drag and drop them to the pumpkins you choose. 1 is your top choice and 4 is your last\n        choice.</li>\n        <li>When you have made all your choices, select the Lock Picks button.</li>\n        <li>Upon lock of your picks, you will receive a ‘WildAlmond’ value.</li>\n        <li>If your value is the highest number (1-5000) on November 5th, you win the prize!</li>\n    </ul>\n    </p>\n\n</br>\n    <p>\n    Thanks for participating! Contact us anytime with your questions or suggestions at support@wildalmonds.com\n    </p>\n</p>\n</br>",
                "author": 21,
