                "title": "How are we going to do this?",
                "blog": "<h1>Hi! I'm from WildAlmonds...</h1><p><br></p><p>...and I'm curious how technology is working for you?</p><p><br></p><p>I've talked to countless customers with just this introduction. Many of the challenges presented were really challenging problems. Our focus has always been on the direct interaction between tasters of wine and the wineries directly.</p><p><br></p><h2>Tasters of wine:</h2><p>Help me </p><ul><li>easily find tasting rooms</li><li>make it accessible on my mobile device</li><li>don't make me download an app</li><li>keep track of the wines I really like</li><li>add comments for each product </li></ul><h2><br></h2><h2>Wineries:</h2><p>We need to improve</p><ul><li>engagement with our new and existing customers</li><li>get feedback from tasters without interrupting the casual experience</li><li>target our sales and promotional campaigns</li><li>communicate more easily with new and existing loyal customers</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>This is quite a list for a regular company let alone a very, very small one.  How'd we do it?  Sign up below and bookmark this page to keep in touch with our blog.  </p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2><br></h2><h2> </h2><p><br></p>",
